2. cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture) - The paper focuses on multi-user wireless networks, which falls under the domain of networking and internet architecture. 
3. cs.SY (Systems and Control) - The paper discusses the role of a relay in achieving interference-free performance, which is a control problem. 
4. cs.MM (Multimedia) - The paper mentions the use of MIMO (Multiple-Input Multiple-Output) technology, which is commonly used in multimedia applications. 
5. cs.CE (Computational Engineering, Finance, and Science) - The paper involves the use of mathematical models and optimization techniques to derive an outer bound and develop a novel scheme, which falls under the domain of computational engineering.
